Hello!

I'm currently using node v18.18.0, react v18.2.0, react-router-dom v6.22.2 and vite.

Previously, icons were rendering without any issues on the FeedMainPage, but they are not rendering correctly on the path that includes `:feedId`. Here are the router information and the icon component.

```tsx
